    content: # PatternFly 5 вҶ’ PatternFly 6: Complete Migration Checklist

> **Source**: Official PatternFly upgrade guide (https://www.patternfly.org/get-started/upgrade/), PF6 release notes, and pf-codemods README.
>
> **Prerequisite**: Complete the PatternFly 5 upgrade process first before migrating to PF6.

---

## Table of Contents
1. [Migration Steps Overview](#1-migration-steps-overview)
2. [Package Changes](#2-package-changes)
3. [Codemods Setup & Usage](#3-codemods-setup--usage)
4. [Removed/Deprecated Components](#4-removeddeprecated-components)
5. [Component API Changes (Alphabetical)](#5-component-api-changes-alphabetical)
6. [Charts Migration](#6-charts-migration)
7. [CSS/Token Changes](#7-csstoken-changes)
8. [Import Path Changes](#8-import-path-changes)
9. [Icon Changes](#9-icon-changes)
10. [Theming Changes](#10-theming-changes)
11. [Breakpoint Changes](#11-breakpoint-changes)
12. [Test Failures to Expect](#12-test-failures-to-expect)
13. [What Codemods Handle vs Manual Work](#13-what-codemods-handle-vs-manual-work)

---

## 1. Migration Steps Overview

1. Update dependencies from PF5 to PF6
2. Run codemods suite (`npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6`)
3. Run with `--fix` flag to auto-fix
4. Remove all CSS overrides (they target outdated PF5 variables)
5. Run class-name-updater codemod (`pf-v5` вҶ’ `pf-v6`)
6. Run tokens-update codemod (CSS variables & React tokens)
7. Run css-vars-updater codemod (for .css/.scss/.md files)
8. Update pixel-based breakpoint logic to rem units
9. Manual cleanup of remaining issues
10. Run `--only data-codemods-cleanup` to remove `data-codemods` attributes

---

## 2. Package Changes

### Core Packages (update versions to v6)
| Package | Notes |
|---------|-------|
| `@patternfly/react-core` | Major version bump to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-table` | Major version bump to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-charts` | Major version bump; Victory charts moved to `/victory` subpath |
| `@patternfly/react-icons` | Major version bump to v6 |
| `@patternfly/react-tokens` | Major version bump; token naming completely changed |
| `@patternfly/react-styles` | Major version bump to v6 |
| `@patternfly/patternfly` | CSS package, major version bump |
| `@patternfly/react-component-groups` | Many component renames |
| `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` | **New package** вҖ” replaces deprecated DragDrop from react-core |

### Victory (Charts) вҖ” Now Optional Peer Dependency
```bash
# Install one of:
npm install victory                    # Full Victory package
# OR install specific packages:
npm install victory-core victory-tooltip  # Only what you need
```

---

## 3. Codemods Setup & Usage

### Main codemods command
```bash
# Dry run (lint-like output):
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6

# Auto-fix:
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --fix

# For large codebases:
NODE_OPTIONS=--max-old-space-size=4096 npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --fix

# Run specific rule only:
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --only <rule-name>

# Final cleanup (run ONCE after all other codemods):
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path-to-src> --v6 --only data-codemods-cleanup --fix
```

### Additional codemods for CSS/tokens
```bash
# Class name updater (pf-v5 вҶ’ pf-v6 in class names):
npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <path> --v6 --fix   # (class-name-updater package)

# CSS variables updater (for .css, .scss, .md files):
# See https://github.com/patternfly/pf-codemods/tree/main/packages/css-vars-updater
```

---

## 4. Removed/Deprecated Components

### Fully Removed (no PF6 equivalent component вҖ” manual migration required)
| Removed Component | Recommended Replacement | Codemod? |
|---|---|---|
| **Application Launcher** (deprecated) | Custom menu with `Menu`/`MenuToggle` | вқҢ No вҖ” manual |
| **Context Selector** (deprecated) | Custom menu with `Menu`/`MenuToggle` | вқҢ No вҖ” manual |
| **Dropdown** (old deprecated version) | New composable `Dropdown` or Dropdown template | вқҢ No вҖ” manual |
| **Options Menu** (deprecated) | New composable `Select` or Select template | вқҢ No вҖ” manual |
| **Page Header** (deprecated) | `Masthead` + `Toolbar` | вқҢ No вҖ” manual |
| **Select** (old deprecated version) | New composable `Select` or Select template | вқҢ No вҖ” manual |
| **KebabToggle** | `MenuToggle` with `variant="plain"` + `EllipsisVIcon` | вң… Yes |
| **PageNavigation** | Removed entirely, use `PageSection` | вң… Yes (removes component) |

### Deprecated (moved to `@patternfly/react-core/deprecated`)
| Component | Replacement | Codemod? |
|---|---|---|
| **Chip** / **ChipGroup** | `Label` / `LabelGroup` | вң… Yes вҖ” moves import; also has rule to replace with Label/LabelGroup |
| **Tile** | `Card` (new Card-as-Tile example) | вң… Yes вҖ” moves import |
| **DragDrop** / **Droppable** / **Draggable** | `DragDropSort` from `@patternfly/react-drag-drop` | вң… Yes вҖ” moves import |
| **DualListSelector** (old) | New `DualListSelector` (promoted from `/next`) | вң… Yes |
| **Modal** (old) | New `Modal` (promoted from `/next`) | вң… Yes |

### Renamed Components
| Old Name (PF5) | New Name (PF6) | Codemod? |
|---|---|---|
| `Text` | `Content` | вң… Yes |
| `TextContent` | `Content` | вң… Yes |
| `TextList` | `Content` (with `component` prop) | вң… Yes |
| `TextListItem` | `Content` (with `component` prop) | вң… Yes |
