## 7. CSS/Token Changes

### CSS Class Prefix Change
| Old | New |
|-----|-----|
| `pf-v5-c-*` (components) | `pf-v6-c-*` |
| `pf-v5-l-*` (layouts) | `pf-v6-l-*` |
| `pf-v5-u-*` (utilities) | `pf-v6-u-*` |
| `pf-v5-m-*` (modifiers) | `pf-v6-m-*` (some renamed) |

**Codemod**: вң… Yes вҖ” `class-name-updater` tool with `--v6 --fix`

### Design Token Variable Migration (MAJOR)

The entire CSS variable system has been overhauled:

| Category | Old Pattern | New Pattern |
|----------|-------------|-------------|
| Global variables | `--pf-v5-global--*` | `--pf-t--global--*` |
| Component variables | `--pf-v5-c-<component>--*` | `--pf-v6-c-<component>--*` |
| Font size | `--pf-v5-global--FontSize--lg` | `--pf-t--global--font--size--lg` |
| Spacing | `--pf-v5-global--spacer--xl` | `--pf-t--global--spacer--xl` |
| Colors | `--pf-v5-global--Color--100` | `--pf-t--global--text--color--regular` (context-specific) |
| Border width | `--pf-v5-global--BorderWidth--lg` | `--pf-t--global--border--width--extra-strong` |
| Box shadow | `--pf-v5-global--BoxShadow--sm` | `--pf-t--global--box-shadow--sm` |
| Z-index | `--pf-v5-global--ZIndex--lg` | `--pf-t--global--z-index--lg` |
| Font weight | `--pf-v5-global--FontWeight--normal` | `--pf-t--global--font--weight--body--default` |

### React Tokens
| Old Pattern | New Pattern |
|-------------|-------------|
| `global_FontSize_lg` | `t_global_font_size_lg` |
| `global_Color_100` | `t_temp_dev_tbd` вҡ пёҸ (requires manual replacement) |
| `global_BorderWidth_lg` | `global_border_width_extra_strong` |
| `c_badge_PaddingLeft` | Needs manual lookup |

**Key**: React tokens whose CSS value starts with `--pf-t` are now prefixed with `t_`

### Codemod Behavior for Tokens
| Token Type | Codemod Behavior |
|------------|-----------------|
| Global non-color tokens (spacers, font-size, box-shadow) | вң… Auto-fixed to closest match |
| Global color tokens | вҡ пёҸ Replaced with `t_temp_dev_tbd` / `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` (hot pink) вҖ” **must be manually replaced** |
| Component tokens (`c_*`) | вқҢ Not auto-fixed вҖ” manual lookup required |
| Chart tokens | вқҢ Not auto-fixed вҖ” manual lookup required |

### Reference Spreadsheets
- [Removed variables](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=1160160856&single=true)
- [Added variables](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vQqeH7ThYi0jkhYEB8B2SXa7x8AaY5T9ajG6o-Ogz3p7YVp0OuTulb_L3DYLDrHlY4zUE3IBiup6tkN/pubhtml?gid=268831450&single=true)
- [All PF6 tokens](https://www.patternfly.org/tokens/all-patternfly-tokens)

