<h2 id="detailed">рҹ”Қ Detailed Analysis</h2>

<!-- 6.1 Modal Migration -->
<details id="detail-modal">
  <summary>
    <span>рҹҡӘ Deprecated Modal Migration (Highest Impact)</span>
    <span class="winner-tag">Winner: Goose</span>
  </summary>
  <div class="detail-content">
    <h4>What changed in PF6</h4>
    <p>The old <code>Modal</code> component (with <code>title</code>, <code>actions</code>, <code>header</code> props) was deprecated.
       The new PF6 Modal uses a composable pattern with <code>&lt;ModalHeader&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;ModalBody&gt;</code>, and <code>&lt;ModalFooter&gt;</code> sub-components.
       The old Modal was moved to <code>@patternfly/react-core/deprecated</code>; the new one lives at <code>@patternfly/react-core</code>.</p>

    <h4>Before (PF5 deprecated pattern)</h4>
    <pre><code>import { Modal, ModalVariant } from '@patternfly/react-core/deprecated';

&lt;Modal
  title="Debug information"
  variant={ModalVariant.medium}
  isOpen={isOpen}
  onClose={onClose}
  actions={[&lt;Button onClick={onClose}&gt;Close&lt;/Button&gt;]}
&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Content here...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/Modal&gt;</code></pre>

    <h4>After (PF6 composable pattern)</h4>
    <pre><code>import { Modal, ModalBody, ModalFooter, ModalHeader, ModalVariant } from '@patternfly/react-core';

&lt;Modal
  variant={ModalVariant.medium}
  isOpen={isOpen}
  onClose={onClose}
&gt;
  &lt;ModalHeader title="Debug information" /&gt;
  &lt;ModalBody&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;Content here...&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/ModalBody&gt;
  &lt;ModalFooter&gt;
    &lt;Button onClick={onClose}&gt;Close&lt;/Button&gt;
  &lt;/ModalFooter&gt;
&lt;/Modal&gt;</code></pre>

    <h4>Branch Comparison</h4>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Metric</th><th>pf-codemods-053126-1704</th><th>semver/goose/053126-1509</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Files migrated</td><td style="color:var(--red);">0 / 15</td><td style="color:var(--green);">7 / 15</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Uses ModalHeader/Body/Footer</td><td style="color:var(--red);">No</td><td style="color:var(--green);">Yes вҖ” all 7 files</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Imports from <code>@patternfly/react-core</code> (not deprecated)</td><td style="color:var(--red);">No change</td><td style="color:var(--green);">Yes вҖ” all 7 files</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Build deprecated warnings reduced</td><td style="color:var(--red);">No (10вҶ’10)</td><td style="color:var(--green);">Yes (10вҶ’6)</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h4>Evidence: Goose's Modal migrations (verified correct)</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><code>DebugInformation.tsx</code> вҖ” Full composable Modal with ModalHeader, ModalBody, ModalFooter. Buttons moved from <code>actions</code> prop to ModalFooter children.</li>
      <li><code>AccessLogModal.tsx</code> вҖ” ModalHeader with title and description. ModalBody wraps content.</li>
      <li><code>IstioActionsDropdown.tsx</code> вҖ” Confirm delete dialog uses ModalHeader("Confirm Delete"), ModalBody, ModalFooter with confirm/cancel buttons.</li>
      <li><code>FileAttachment.tsx</code> вҖ” Full migration including dynamic title (<code>action.title || fileName</code>).</li>
      <li><code>SessionTimeout.tsx</code> вҖ” Clean migration, buttons array вҶ’ ModalFooter children.</li>
      <li><code>TimeDurationModal.tsx</code> вҖ” ModalHeader, ModalBody, ModalFooter all present.</li>
      <li><code>ServiceInsights.tsx</code> вҖ” Metrics management modal correctly migrated.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</details>

<!-- 6.2 Button Icon -->
<details id="detail-button">
  <summary>
    <span>рҹ”ҳ Button Icon Prop Migration</span>
    <span class="winner-tag">Winner: Goose</span>
  </summary>
  <div class="detail-content">
    <h4>What changed in PF6</h4>
    <p>For <code>variant="plain"</code> buttons, icons must now be passed via the <code>icon</code> prop instead of as children.
       The official PF codemods handle this automatically for <code>variant="plain"</code> buttons.</p>
    <pre><code>// PF5:
&lt;Button variant="plain"&gt;&lt;CopyIcon /&gt;&lt;/Button&gt;

// PF6:
&lt;Button variant="plain" icon={&lt;CopyIcon /&gt;} /&gt;</code></pre>

    <h4>Branch Comparison</h4>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Metric</th><th>pf-codemods-053126-1704</th><th>semver/goose/053126-1509</th></tr></thead>
