  <div class="detail-content">
    <h4>What changed in PF6</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><code>DropdownGroup</code> children must be wrapped in <code>&lt;DropdownList&gt;</code></li>
      <li><code>MenuToggle</code> icon-only toggles should use the <code>icon</code> prop</li>
      <li><code>popperProps={{ position: 'right' }}</code> вҶ’ <code>popperProps={{ placement: 'bottom-end' }}</code> or <code>appendTo: 'inline'</code></li>
      <li>InputGroup items should be wrapped in <code>&lt;InputGroupItem&gt;</code></li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Changes by Goose</h4>
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>File</th><th>Change</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><code>NamespaceActions.tsx</code></td><td>DropdownGroup children вҶ’ DropdownList wrapper; MenuToggle icon prop</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>LoadingWizardActionsDropdownGroup.tsx</code></td><td>DropdownItem wrapped in DropdownList inside DropdownGroup</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>stylesComponentFactory.tsx</code></td><td>DropdownGroup children вҶ’ DropdownList wrapper</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>NotificationCenter.tsx</code></td><td>DropdownList wrapping for actions; popperProps position вҶ’ placement</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>HelpDropdown.tsx</code></td><td>MenuToggle icon prop; popperProps position вҶ’ appendTo</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>ServiceWizardDropdown.tsx</code></td><td>Removed unnecessary DropdownList wrapper (children is a DropdownGroup)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>K8sFilterBuilder.tsx</code></td><td>Wrapped Dropdown/TextInput siblings in InputGroupItem (304-line refactor)</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>K8sMatchBuilder.tsx</code></td><td>Same InputGroupItem wrapping pattern</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p><strong>Codemods branch:</strong> No Dropdown or MenuToggle changes.</p>

    <h4>вҡ пёҸ Goose Concern: ServiceWizardDropdown.tsx</h4>
    <p>Goose removed the <code>&lt;DropdownList&gt;</code> wrapper from ServiceWizardDropdown and passed <code>&lt;ServiceWizardActionsDropdownGroup&gt;</code> directly as a Dropdown child. This component renders <code>&lt;DropdownGroup&gt;</code> elements, which in PF6 <em>should</em> be wrapped in <code>&lt;DropdownList&gt;</code>. This removal may cause rendering issues. However, since the build passes and the pattern is used elsewhere in PF6 examples, the risk is moderate.</p>
